latestPosts.caption:
Only Gratitude Roadies XX
On a random day I decide to show up for an audition that hasnt exactly been a dream but a fun Sunday thingy till then! A few days later I realise it has become a life goal, post the experience.
Roadies is not just a show, it is an experience, an emotion, a dream, no wonder people have been auditioning for 10+ years there.
You haven’t seen the best of me yet though🧿 

I don’t know if the episode will ever be aired, and I hope not because I wish to be on the journey when you all see my PI, clearly not this season, but soon! 
Have learnt a tonne lot from this, 
Thanks a lot @rhea_chakraborty @nehadhupia @princenarula @elvish_raosahab__ @rannvijaysingha 

Strange how some events in life impact your life’s journey and change the course of it entirely💪
